Image Prompt:
Create a captivating and awe-inspiring image of a divine figure surrounded by radiant light, performing miraculous acts. The scene should depict a serene and sacred atmosphere, showcasing the power and grace of a God of miracles. Include subtle symbols of faith and hope, such as a dove or rays of light, to emphasize the spiritual significance of the moment. The image should evoke a sense of wonder and reverence, resonating with viewers on a deep, emotional level.
